      <title>Vista 和 Blackstone 寻求为 Smartsheet 筹集 32 亿美元私募债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/vista-blackstone-seek-3-2-billion-private-debt-for-smartsheet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Vista Equity Partners 和 Blackstone Inc. 正在向私人信贷机构申请 32 亿美元的债务方案，以支持其对软件制造商 Smartsheet Inc. 的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/vista-blackstone-seek-3-2-billion-private-debt-for-smartsheet</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 15:15:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
