      <title>Ares 表示正在与 GLP Capital Partners 就交易进行深入谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ares-is-said-in-advanced-talks-on-deal-with-glp-capital-partners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Ares Management Corp. 正就收购 GLP Capital Partners Ltd. 中国以外的业务进行深入谈判，此次收购可能成为另类资产管理行业近期最大的并购案之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ares-is-said-in-advanced-talks-on-deal-with-glp-capital-partners</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 15:01:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
